Class Pet

java.lang.Object
model.Pet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Pet extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a pet with various attributes such as name, age, species, and more. Implements Serializable for object serialization.
Version:
1.0
Author:
